      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KALANI CRUISE (2) placed two runs ago then again in the money last time when second (29.89) at The Gardens in a Maiden. With a good start should be able to take advantage of the low draw. Better than last run and makes appeal this time. CONFUSION REIGNS (7) got a clear run and led until the final stages when second and beaten 9 lengths (30.24) at this track in a Maiden over 520m. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Will give a great sight again. MARISSA VELLA (6) was below best at her last start when 6th at this track following a second place finish (30.65) there two back. Has good speed so she should be prominent despite the draw. Can figure in the finish. SHE'S MAYHEM (8) is a newcomer from the Tomas Rees kennel. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Profiles well so watch market closely.",
